H0.text: Which British swimmer won Olympic Gold Medals in 2008 in the 400 and 800 m freestyle. Joanne Jackson

H1.text: Which British swimmer won Olympic Gold Medals in 2008 in the 400 and 800 m freestyle. Caitlin McClatchey

H2.text: Which British swimmer won Olympic Gold Medals in 2008 in the 400 and 800 m freestyle. Keri-anne Payne

H3.text: Which British swimmer won Olympic Gold Medals in 2008 in the 400 and 800 m freestyle. Becky Adlington

A4.text: She won two gold medals at the 2008 Summer Olympics in the 400-metre freestyle and 800-metre freestyle.

A5.text: She was the first British swimmer to win two Olympic gold medals since 1908.
